Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:05.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想呼唤着明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂的呼唤  LET'S GO PASSION
