Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S  GO  激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.95,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『像热血动画般』去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的抚子是总集篇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是像介绍篇一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事也进行到转折点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要一集用来整理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚啊  纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是因为制作公司面临除夕忙不过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去  丈真现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.20,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子放送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快点集合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是抚子的神秘时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特别告诉你有关抚子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2l95年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球面临最大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体疏散!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以本舰撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的无人兵器军团攻击并占领火星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更攻下了月球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.91,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至逼近地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联合军也似乎毫无办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这就轮到抚子出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NERGAL重工独自开发机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形式NERGAL  ND-001
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全长298M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全高106.8M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全幅l48M  总重量37530t
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容人员2l4名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配备四座核脉冲引擎  两座相转移引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中枢电脑使用SVC2027  通称思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本诸元大概是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先从位于十二层甲板最上方的舰桥看起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的指令都是从这儿发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今天是假日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥的正下方就是虚拟实境室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间是为了要缓解乘员长期\N出与宇宙空间的精神压力而设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能自动测量各自的脑波还是其他资料进行精神分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后创造出适合那个人的剧情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里设定明人是和我同一个社团的学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  放轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么紧张的话没办法缓解压力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是为了学长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为也有想在日常生活中除去烦恼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也有个冥想室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第四甲板有娱乐室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连2l96年型最新式桌球台也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁有利用雷射投影的展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的风景  气压  氧气浓度可以自由选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那下方的厨房  荷梅今天也在发挥她的手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是年底或过年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说让客人满意也是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们非得认真地加油不可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这不是做生意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我自认手艺不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是职业的  完全不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球看似狭小  其实很广大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每块土地都有那块土地的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是我在臭盖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店抚子食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地球三百个地方的调味料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶叶也收集了最上等的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够在放点酒那就更好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督  不可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要推荐料理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是放了一堆章鱼热狗的火星{\fn黑体\fs25}丼{\r}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人比较喜欢鸡肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谈那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们抚子最骄傲的人行机械人AESTIVALIS的机库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排排站的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小AESTI的事情就交…给…我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从陆战模组开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗？这直拳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃力也出类拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的空战模组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还更厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子的事就交给我凯大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄就是得像这样才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  看看这架势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何能在空中飞就已经帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田  你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后必胜绝技是众所皆知的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超极勾拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没这么沸腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外这AESTIVALIS还有隐藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CROSS CRASH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样世界的和平就安全啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搞什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重装模组的话我坐过和明人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种重量感真叫人受不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OG战模组全部配备了四架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要驾驶员是天河明人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂凉子  天野光  真木泉这四人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的  逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧  十架才打中三架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来蚱蜢的力场好像被强化了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会进化的机器?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比近战是我的本行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  天河怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候来救我们的是最新型的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  是什么  这个模组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新型的啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动机也很小巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连肌肤也滑溜溜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就搞一辈子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个以飞行员身份加入的赤月流行以及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉娜.金城.王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两人好像有什么隐情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份  目的一切不明的无人兵器群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类将这初次遭遇的异星文明称为木星蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用入射角就行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之至今的经历是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法对迅速进化的木星兵器施以重击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画真好啊  充满梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是写实的战斗场面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来会怎么样发展呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了  阿卡拉王子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然无法征服地球吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我正在收集有关地球人文化的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便拟定作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人的资料? 有意思  我静候佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料部分就差不多这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟214人同吃同住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有各式各样事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各式各样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长和天河明人之间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉  真是不好意恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么地方受伤了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来舰长跟天河君是青梅竹马的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经在哪里见过面吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你肚子痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  走开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你一个提起精神的诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  居然在我不清楚的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明平常忙起来时都是我代理百合香工作的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  冷静下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊… 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这两个看来真是很速配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了什么才来火星的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从上了抚子之后这还是你第一次对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以…吻我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香  你在胡说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  只要你吻我我会再加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会比现在更稍微卖力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人喜欢我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人有各种复杂的关系  真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  琉璃琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当大人也有很多好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你戴兔子帽很合适哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是真是  有各式各样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有”好事”吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷  大人的好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河天河天河…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载满各种想法前进的机动战舰抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后又将去哪里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人恋爱的命运又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真希望我能跟阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  阿卡拉大人看起来好像对我没兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收集到关于地球人文化的情报了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部叫"机动战舰抚子"的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是调查地球人用的最好样本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把故事用图来表现的地球人的娱乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  虚构故事这些脱离现实的东西真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  天河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人也有男人跟女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中萌芽的淡淡的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么爱呀恋情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事就能够打赢吗  下等的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是什么  米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫做次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种用护罩进行的敌阵突破攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠反作用力突破敌阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到可以在这种地方发现打败激钢人的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  米耶米耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人专用机大阿卡拉SPECIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命出动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人你等着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的飞行物体正急速迫近研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做也没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元歪曲防壁!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑  丈  明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们立刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来的话我要下杀手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GEKIGER IN！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西对我没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电浆断！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩具般的东西破不了这次元歪曲防壁的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  激钢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  这样下去会败的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然才刚完成还未测试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这地步只好一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑  丈  明  用激钢爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆炎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我为了防范于未然秘密开发的激钢爆炎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果没有一气呵成激钢人会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话也只能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢爆炎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个光芒是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点逃啊  卡拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  地球人给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候想出那种武器的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子在抚子里演的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士也在看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年夜面正等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面  也有年糕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是明天才吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？这种结束方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此  下集也请继续收看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是配御统百合香的桑岛法子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然低温每天持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观赏机动战舰抚子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把冷风什么的用次元歪曲防壁吹散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:22:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着下集木星蜥蜴的真面目似乎终于明了了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的故事呢？我现在就好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香还有出场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下集机动战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自遥远星球的『男友』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.96,0:22:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说定喽
